  "content": "t-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-purple);\">LLM Chat</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 8px;\">llama.cpp</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Arrow down to bottleneck -->\n  <div class=\"arrow-down\">&#11015;</div>\n  <!-- RTX 3060 — bottleneck -->\n  <div style=\"background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.08); border: 3px solid var(--accent-red); border-radius: 20px; padding: 28px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; position: relative;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent-red); margin-bottom: 4px;\">RTX 3060</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary);\">6 GB VRAM, constantly swapping</div>\n    <div style=\"position: absolute; top: -14px; right: 32px; background: var(--accent-red); color: white; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; padding: 4px 14px; border-radius: 8px; letter-spacing: 1px;\">BOTTLENECK</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Idle Intel -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; margin-top: 16px;\">\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; background: var(--bg-card); border: 2px dashed var(--text-muted); border-radius: 20px; padding: 28px; text-align: center; opacity: 0.5;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 32px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--text-muted);\">Intel Iris Xe</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px;\">Completely idle</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"font-size: 64px;\">&#128564;</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">02 / 08</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SLIDE 3: THE ARCHITECTURE — mostly visual already -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">The Fix</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 48px;\">\n    Split Them.<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-green\">One GPU Each.</span>\n  </div>",
